;\n  const limit = query.limit ?? 20;\n  ...\n```\n\nWait, the `RecommendationQu
eryDto` has `limit?: number = 20;` which means it\'s both optional AND has a def
ault value. But then the service also does `const limit = query.limit ?? 20;`. T
his is redundant but not harmful.\n\nLet me look at another thing. In `matching.
